   International

   International Relations

   The International office at Institut d'Optique manages exchange and
   double-degrees agreements with international partners, as well as
   international admissions and study abroad applications.

   Contacts:
     * Pierre BALADI (Mr), Head of International Relations:
       pierre[dot]baladi[at]institutoptique[dot]fr
     * Sita BABY (Ms), Deputy Head of International Relations:
       sita[dot]baby[at]institutoptique[dot]fr

   or: international@institutoptique.fr

   Address:

   Institut d'Optique Graduate School

   Relations internationales

   2 avenue Augustin Fresnel

   91127 Palaiseau cedex

   FRANCE

International partners

   Agreements for study (outgoing and incoming) have been signed with the
   following establishments:

Europe (exchange studies):

     * Be-Université de Liège
     * De-HAWK (University of Applied Sciences and Arts)
     * De-Universität Stuttgart
     * Es-Universidad de Murcia
     * Pl-WUT - Warsaw University of Technology (Politechnika Warszawska)
     * Se-KTH Royal Institute of Technology (exchange and double-degree)

Brazil:

     * Br-Instituto de Fisica de São Carlos da Universidade de São Paulo
     * Br-Escola Politecnica da Universidade de São Paulo (EP-USP)
     * Br-Escola de Engenharia de São Carlos - Universidade de São Paulo
       (EESC-USP)

China:

     * Cn-East China Normal University, Shanghai & Institut d'Optique
       Graduate School

Japan:

     * Jp-School of Engineering Science, Osaka University

Russia:

     * Ru-ITMO University, Saint Petersburg
     * Ru-Moscow State University, Bauman
     * Ru-Novosibirsk State University
     * Ru-Tomsk Polytechnic University

